00:40:18.479 --> 00:40:19.480
Hindi ko maintindihan.

00:40:19.980 --> 00:40:22.107
Paano magiging guro ang isang taong ganito kasama?

00:40:33.953 --> 00:40:34.995
Natatakot ka?

00:40:35.871 --> 00:40:36.747
Kaya alam mo ang takot?

00:40:40.084 --> 00:40:41.627
Sige, maging mas mayabang ka.

00:40:42.211 --> 00:40:43.045
Maghintay ka lang.

00:40:43.128 --> 00:40:45.839
Puwede akong magsumbong
sa'yo ng ilang bagay sa susunod na linggo.

00:40:45.923 --> 00:40:48.759
Kapag hiniling ng paaralan sa lola mo
na alisin ka sa paaralan,

00:40:49.343 --> 00:40:51.011
tignan natin kung mayabang ka pa.

00:41:28.924 --> 00:41:30.926
Ang hirap naman talagang lunukin 'yan, 'di ba?

00:41:34.638 --> 00:41:35.931
Kung gayon,

00:41:37.099 --> 00:41:38.684
